LiberationSans-Regular.ttf
==========================

Liberation Sans (Regular) — used by the artboard PDF export (ADR 0035) as the
embedded text face. Chosen because it covers Latin + Cyrillic (incl. Ukrainian
є/ї/ґ) + Greek in a single TTF, so multilingual captions (en/uk/ru) render
without glyph fallback ("tofu").

